#. <section class="sutta" id="sn15.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Sukhitasutta"
msgstr "12. In a Good Way"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.187"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.12:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.2"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro … pe …"
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning. …"

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.3"
msgid ""
"yaṃ, bhikkhave, passeyyātha sukhitaṃ susajjitaṃ, niṭṭhamettha gantabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"When you see someone in a good way, in a happy state, you should conclude:"

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.4"
msgid "‘amhehipi evarūpaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ iminā dīghena addhunā’ti."
msgstr "‘In all this long time, we too have undergone the same thing.’"

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.6"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro."
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. …"

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.7"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.8"
msgid "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and "
"freed regarding all conditions.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.12:1.9"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
